--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.0.1 (2018-03-08)
I: Allow additional key exchange algorithms and message authentication codes

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
I: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.2.2 (2017-12-08)
I: Ensure role works in check mode

* Version 1.2.1 (2017-11-24)
B: Remove unsupported option 'PrintLastLog' on FreeBSD

* Version 1.2.0 (2017-10-18)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.2
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.1

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.19.0 (2017-04-16)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.0

* Version 0.18.0 (2017-02-28)
F: Add 'openssh_x11_display_offset' option to configure 'X11DisplayOffset'

* Version 0.17.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.16.0 (2016-09-03)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.0
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.15.1 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.15.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.14.1 (2016-04-17)
B: Remove 'VersionAddendum' parameter from 'ssh_config'

* Version 0.14.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.13.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8
F: Add support for 'openssh_version_addendum' option

* Version 0.12.0 (2016-02-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.11.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.10.1 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.10.0 (2015-11-16)
F: Update 'Gentoo' configuration files

* Version 0.9.0 (2015-08-13)
F: Update 'Gentoo' configuration files

* Version 0.8.1 (2015-02-09)
I: Improve OpenSSH validation

* Version 0.8.0 (2015-01-08)
F: Add options to harden OpenSSH configuration

* Version 0.7.2 (2014-12-30)
I: Add handler for validating OpenSSH configuration

* Version 0.7.1 (2014-12-22)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.7.0 (2014-12-07)
F: Add option 'openssh_match' to override settings

* Version 0.6.0 (2014-11-23)
F: Update configuration files to FreeBSD version '10.1-RELEASE'

* Version 0.5.1 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.5.0 (2014-08-25)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.3.2 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-07-22)
I: Improve SSH client options to prevent SSH MITM (Downgrade) Attack

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-07-07)
F: Add support for 'UseDNS' option

* Version 0.2.3 (2014-05-26)
B: Fix issue with 'openssh_print_motd' (PrintMotd) option

* Version 0.2.2 (2014-05-26)
B: Move file configuration from 'install' to 'enable' task

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-05-26)
I: Change default value of 'openssh_print_motd' (PrintMotd) option

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-05-05)
F: Add support for running OpenSSH on multiple ports

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-04-28)
F: Initial release
